# Careervexa - MERN Stack Job Board Application ğŸ’¼

**Careervexa** is a full-stack job board web application that connects job seekers and employers. Users can create profiles, search and apply for jobs, post job listings, and communicate via real-time chat â€” all built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) with Socket.IO integration for live messaging.

> Built with ğŸ’™ as part of a 6-week MERN Full Stack Web Development course project.

---

## ğŸš€ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React + Vite
- TailwindCSS
- Axios
- React Router
- React Toastify

### Backend
- Node.js + Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- JWT Authentication
- Socket.IO

### Real-Time Chat
- One-on-one messaging
- Typing indicators
- Delivered & Read ticks (like WhatsApp)
- Unread message count
- Media upload preview

